headline: CSX Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer to Address UBS Global Industrials and Transportation Conference
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., Nov. 25, 2024 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- CSX Corp. (NASDAQ: CSX) Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer, Sean Pelkey, will address the 2024 UBS Global Industrials and Transportation Conference in Palm Beach on Wednesday, December 4, at 8:00 a.m. Eastern Time. This address will be broadcast live via webcast at http://investors.csx.com. A replay will be available following the conclusion of this event.
